content: 0xbbjoker: This week, 0xbbjoker focused on maintenance and bug fixes, merging a fix for an issue in the OpenAI plugin (elizaos-plugins/plugin-openai#16) and removing a significant amount of unused code in elizaos/eliza#6029. They also supported the team by reviewing 2 PRs and commenting on an issue. Their activity shows a primary focus on bug fixes and configuration file changes across the codebase.
